The paper introduces a new model for relational reasoning, which involves modeling entities and their relations in a document. This falls under the broad category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The model is a neural network with memory augmentation, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The model is trained end-to-end, which is also a common approach in neural network training (cs.NE). Finally, the model is tested on question-answering tasks, which often involve computer vision and image understanding (cs.CV).
